## Release 0.5.0 (2025-09-24)

* update to nbxmpp 5, pygobject 3.50
* move from build.py to pyproject.toml


## Release 0.4.0 (2023-08-02)

* update to nbxmpp 4, PyGObject 3.40
* update docs
* fix config validation
* config must be explicitly created and passed to start
* add 'ready()' callback method: called when the bot is connected and logged in and ready to send/receive messages

## Release 0.3.1 (2020-04-26)

* Fix docs and readme

## Release 0.3.0 (2020-04-26)

### Features
* stop loop on uncaught exceptions
* add a preconfigured logger in bot class
* set logger format


